### DeliverEats API – test from Cursor/VS Code (REST Client)
### Install extension: "REST Client" by Huachao Mao (id: humao.rest-client)
### Then click "Send Request" above any line that starts with ###

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### API v1 welcome
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### 404 (should return error JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/unknown

### ----- Auth: Admin (cookies) -----
### Admin login (sets accessToken + refreshToken cookies)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@delivereats.com", "password": "Admin@123!" }

### Admin refresh (send cookies)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/admin/refresh

### Admin logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/admin/logout

### ----- Auth: Customer (phone OTP) — send-otp + verify-otp -----
### Customer send-otp
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/customer/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{ "phone": "+252618889456" }

### Customer verify-otp (paste otp from send-otp response in dev)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/customer/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{ "phone": "+252618889456", "otp": "1234" }

### Customer refresh (paste refreshToken from verify-otp response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/customer/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN" }

### Customer logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/customer/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN" }
